### ğŸ“Œ Part 3: Custom Python Library
- **Library name:** `alumathgroup13`  
- Supports matrix multiplication for matrices of any dimension  
- Error handling included  
- Pure Python (no external math libraries like NumPy)  
- Published on PyPI  
